    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这是学习《数学建模算法与应用》司守奎版-第7章《数理统计》后整理的笔记pwq    </p><p>matlab代码可直接cv ( •̀ ω •́ )✧</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="区间估计"><a href="#区间估计" class="headerlink" title="区间估计"></a>区间估计</h1><h2 id="已知总体均值"><a href="#已知总体均值" class="headerlink" title="已知总体均值"></a>已知总体均值</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab"><span class="token comment">%正态分布，根据已知平均值置信水平求置信区间</span>clc<span class="token punctuation">,</span>clearx0<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1050</span> <span class="token number">1100</span> <span class="token number">1120</span> <span class="token number">1250</span> <span class="token number">1280</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">'</span>pd<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitdist</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x0<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Normal'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%对数据进行正态分布拟合</span>ci<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">paramci</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>pd<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Alpha'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0.1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%置信水平为0.9，ci的第一列为均值的置信区间</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="未知总体均值及方差"><a href="#未知总体均值及方差" class="headerlink" title="未知总体均值及方差"></a>未知总体均值及方差</h2><p>假设测定值总体的 $\mu$、$\sigma^2$未知，已知测定观察值为6.683,6.681,6.676.6.6678,6.679,6.672</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">clc clear x1<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">6.683</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6.681</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6.676</span><span class="token number">.6</span><span class="token number">.6678</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6.679</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">6.672</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>h1<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p1<span class="token punctuation">,</span>ci1<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st1<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">ttest</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x1<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token function">mean</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Alpha'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0.1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%均值检验和区间估计，ci1是均值的置信区间，置信水平0.9</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>h2<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p2<span class="token punctuation">,</span>ci2<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st2<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">vartest</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x1<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token function">var</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x1<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Alpha'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0.1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%方差检验和区间估计</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h1 id="非参数检验"><a href="#非参数检验" class="headerlink" title="非参数检验"></a>非参数检验</h1><ul><li><strong>$X^2$拟合优度检验:</strong> 检验$p_i &#x3D;F_0 (a_i)-F_0(a_i-1)&#x3D;p_i0 (i&#x3D;1,2,…,k) $的正确性，并未直接检验原假设的分布函数$F_0 (x)$的正确性。</li><li><strong>柯尔莫哥洛夫(Kolmogorov-Smirnov)检验:</strong> 检验直接针对原假设 $H_0:F(x)&#x3D;F_0 (x)$,这里的分布函数$F_0 (x)$必须为 <u>连续型分布</u>。</li></ul><p><em>下面来举个栗子~</em></p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">clc<span class="token punctuation">,</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">,</span>alpha<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0.05</span><span class="token comment">%显著性水平0.05</span>a<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">15.8</span> <span class="token number">15.2</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">15.9</span> <span class="token number">14.7</span> <span class="token number">14.8</span> <span class="token number">15.5</span> <span class="token number">15.6</span> <span class="token number">15.3</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">15.3</span> <span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">15.6</span> <span class="token number">15.7</span> <span class="token number">14.8</span> <span class="token number">14.5</span> <span class="token number">14.2</span> <span class="token number">14.9</span> <span class="token number">14.9</span> <span class="token number">15.2</span> <span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">15.3</span> <span class="token number">15.6</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">14.9</span> <span class="token number">14.2</span> <span class="token number">14.6</span> <span class="token number">15.8</span> <span class="token number">15.2</span> <span class="token number">15.9</span> <span class="token number">15.2</span> <span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">14.9</span> <span class="token number">14.8</span> <span class="token number">14.5</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">15.5</span> <span class="token number">15.5</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">15.1</span> <span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">15.3</span> <span class="token number">14.7</span> <span class="token number">14.5</span> <span class="token number">15.5</span> <span class="token number">15.0</span> <span class="token number">14.7</span> <span class="token number">14.6</span> <span class="token number">14.2</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>pd<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitdist</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Normal'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%采用x^2拟合优度检验</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>h<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">chi2gof</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'cdf'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>pd<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'NParams'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>k2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">chi2inv</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token operator">-</span>alpha<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st<span class="token punctuation">.</span>df<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%采用柯尔莫哥洛夫检验</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>yn<span class="token punctuation">,</span>xn<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">ecdf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%计算经验分布函数值</span>y<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">cdf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>pd<span class="token punctuation">,</span>xn<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%计算原假设分布值函数</span>Dn<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">max</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">abs</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>yn<span class="token operator">-</span>y<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%计算检验统计量D_n的值</span>LJ<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">1.36</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token function">sqrt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">length</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%计算拒绝域的临界值，1.36由显著性水平0.05所确定</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>h<span class="token punctuation">,</span>p<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st<span class="token punctuation">,</span>cv<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">kstest</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'CDF'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>pd<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%直接调用工具箱函数进行KS检验</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><ul><li><strong>$X^2$拟合优度检验:</strong> 算出自由度df&#x3D;4,查$X^2$分布表，得$X_{0.05} ^{2} (4)$&#x3D;9.4877,代码运算结果k2&#x3D;5.0318（即$X^2$）,故假设$H_0$成立,即符合正态分布。   </li><li><strong>柯尔莫哥洛夫(Kolmogorov-Smirnov)检验:</strong> Dn&#x3D;0.0797 &lt; LJ&#x3D;0.1923,故原假设成立</li></ul><h1 id="方差分析"><a href="#方差分析" class="headerlink" title="方差分析"></a>方差分析</h1><p>方差分析是<u>用数理统计分析实验结果，鉴别各因素对结果的影响程度</u>。     </p><p>方差分析一般用于检验不同的样本是否具有显著差异。例如不同工艺制成的灯泡，寿命是否有显著差异。再如用几种化肥和几种小麦品种在若干块试验田里种植小麦，推断不同化肥和品种对小麦产量有无显著影响。</p><h2 id="单因素方差分析方法"><a href="#单因素方差分析方法" class="headerlink" title="单因素方差分析方法"></a>单因素方差分析方法</h2><p><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic1.png" alt="方差分析表"></p><ul><li><strong>$\alpha$:</strong> 显著性水平</li><li><strong>原假设$H_0$:</strong> 需要观测的因素A取不同水平时，指标无显著差异。（若干总体均值相等）即该因素对实验结果没有显著影响。</li><li><strong>拒接原假设的条件:</strong> $F$&gt;$F_\alpha (r-1,n-r)$  或者  p&lt;$\alpha$</li><li><strong>$S_A$:</strong> 各组均值对总平均值的偏差平方和，即组间平方和，反映的是A不同水平间的差异。</li><li><strong>$S_E$:</strong> 各组内的数据对样本均值偏差平方和的总和，即组内平方和，反映的是样本观测值和均值的差异，<u>属于随机误差</u>。</li></ul><p>用anoval函数就可以辣！</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab"><span class="token punctuation">[</span>p<span class="token punctuation">,</span>t<span class="token punctuation">,</span>st<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">anoval</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token operator">'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">%注意矩阵转置</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="双因素方差分析方法"><a href="#双因素方差分析方法" class="headerlink" title="双因素方差分析方法"></a>双因素方差分析方法</h2><p>首先要注意两个因素之间有没有交互影响。<br>（果咩 懒得敲公式了TT）    </p><p>至于代码，用anoval2函数即可</p><h3 id="无交互效应"><a href="#无交互效应" class="headerlink" title="无交互效应"></a>无交互效应</h3><p><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic2.png" alt="方差分析表"><br>和单因素方差分析的拒绝条件差不多，只不过分别比较两个因素的影响即可。<br><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic4.png" alt="F检验方法"></p><h3 id="有交互效应"><a href="#有交互效应" class="headerlink" title="有交互效应"></a>有交互效应</h3><p><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic3.png" alt="方差分析表"><br><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic5.png" alt="F检验方法"><br>多了一个判断有无交互关系。</p><h1 id="回归分析"><a href="#回归分析" class="headerlink" title="回归分析"></a>回归分析</h1><h2 id="一元线性回归"><a href="#一元线性回归" class="headerlink" title="一元线性回归"></a>一元线性回归</h2><p>先看散点图–判断为近似线性–先预测出md用于算出残差–再看残差图确定排除阈值–利用残差排除野值–重新建模</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">clc<span class="token punctuation">,</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">,</span>close alla<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">readmatrix</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>"data7_23<span class="token punctuation">.</span>txt"<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>x<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token string">'; y=a(2,:)'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%提取x，y，并且变成列向量</span><span class="token function">subplot</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">121</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token function">plot</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'ko'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>md<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%初次拟合线性回归模型</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>yh<span class="token punctuation">,</span>yhint<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">predict</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>md<span class="token punctuation">,</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%求预测值和置信区间</span><span class="token function">subplot</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">122</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token function">plotResiduals</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>md<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'caseorder'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%画残差图</span>r<span class="token operator">=</span>y<span class="token operator">-</span>yhind<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">find</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">abs</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>r<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">>=</span><span class="token number">1.5</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%求残差及野值编号</span>md2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'Exclude'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>ind<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%排除野值后重新建模</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="一元非线性回归"><a href="#一元非线性回归" class="headerlink" title="一元非线性回归"></a>一元非线性回归</h2><p>唯一不同的就是运用非线性回归模型fitnlm.并且如果规定了方程形式，还需要用匿名函数来定义.</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">clc<span class="token punctuation">,</span>cleard<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span> <span class="token number">2</span> <span class="token number">4</span> <span class="token number">5</span> <span class="token number">7</span> <span class="token number">8</span> <span class="token number">9</span> <span class="token number">10</span>   <span class="token number">1.3</span> <span class="token number">1</span> <span class="token number">0.9</span> <span class="token number">0.81</span> <span class="token number">0.7</span> <span class="token number">0.6</span> <span class="token number">0.55</span> <span class="token number">0.4</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>x<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">d</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token string">';y=d(2,:)'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>fun<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">@</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>a<span class="token punctuation">,</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">./</span>x<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">*</span>x<span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">4</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token operator">.^</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%用匿名函数定义要拟合的函数</span>a0<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%给回归系数赋初值</span>md<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitnlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span>fun<span class="token punctuation">,</span>a0<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%拟合非线性回归模型</span>a_ci<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">coefCI</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>md<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%求拟合参数的置信区间</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>y_pre<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y_ci<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">predict</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>md<span class="token punctuation">,</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%计算y的预测值和置信区间</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="多元非线性回归"><a href="#多元非线性回归" class="headerlink" title="多元非线性回归"></a>多元非线性回归</h2><p>主要体现在匿名函数中x的写法上需要划分x1，x2,…<br>例如<code>fun=@(beta,x) (beta(4)*x(:,2)-x(:,3)/beta(5))./(1+beta(1)*x(:,1)+beta(2)*x(:,2)+beta(3)*x(:,3))</code></p><h2 id="多元二项式回归"><a href="#多元二项式回归" class="headerlink" title="多元二项式回归"></a>多元二项式回归</h2><h3 id="重要工具箱-rstool"><a href="#重要工具箱-rstool" class="headerlink" title="重要工具箱 rstool"></a>重要工具箱 rstool</h3><p><code>rstool(X,Y,model,alpha)</code><br> <em>$\alpha$默认0.05，model默认线性模型</em><br><img src="/2023/08/09/20230809/pic6.png" alt="四种模型"><br>rmse均方误差来衡量模型优劣，beta是回归方程的系数矩阵。</p><h2 id="逐步回归"><a href="#逐步回归" class="headerlink" title="逐步回归"></a>逐步回归</h2><p>逐步回归的作用在于<u><em>从众多变量中挑选出对因变量影响显著的自变量</em></u>.<br>可以分为 <u><em>前进法、后退法、逐步回归法</em></u>.</p><ul><li><strong>前进法:</strong> 从一个变量到全部变量引入。</li><li><strong>后退法:</strong> 从全部变量引入，每次删除系数绝对值最小的变量。</li><li><strong>逐步回归法:</strong> 一个一个引入变量，每次引入后都进行F检验，适当做些变量剔除。<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">clc<span class="token punctuation">,</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">,</span>close alla<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">readmatrix</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'data7_25.txt'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>x<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token keyword">end</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span> y<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">a</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">end</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment">%输入不同的组合尝试qwq</span>md0<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">)</span>md1<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'y~1+x1+x2+x4'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>md2<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">fitlm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'y~1+x1+x2'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">%一步到位</span>md<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token function">stepwiselm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>y<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">'y~1+x1+x2+x3+x4'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
